How CHLG Works

The simple, addictive loop backed by AI verification.

  1. Choose a challenge — fitness, lifestyle, social or trending tasks.
  2. Do it in real life — no filters, no edits, no cheats.
  3. Upload proof — a photo or short video.
  4. AI verifies authenticity — face, motion, behavior, timing and consistency.
  5. Earn CHLG instantly — rewards are delivered directly to your in-app wallet.

One action → one verification → one reward. Repeat daily.

Why Now?

Challenge culture, AI and Web3 have finally aligned – making CHLG possible for the first time.

Challenge culture is already massive — but unrewarded. For years, people have created fitness tasks, dares, trends and social challenges without earning anything for real effort.

Today, three global shifts finally align:

  • AI can verify real human actions at scale — something impossible until now.
  • TikTok/Instagram challenges define how Gen-Z communicates and participates.
  • Web3 rewards make it possible to instantly compensate real-world behavior.
  • Brands want engagement they can trust, not impressions or fake views.

CHLG sits at the intersection of culture, AI and rewards – at the first moment in history when this is truly possible.

What CHLG solves

CHLG converts unrewarded challenge culture into an AI-verified reward layer for real-world behavior.

The problem

Billions of people join challenges, trends and daily actions without owning any of the value they create. Platforms capture attention, data and ad revenue while users get only views and likes.

The CHLG solution

CHLG turns those same actions into crypto rewards. Users complete real-life challenges, AI verifies authenticity, and rewards are paid out on-chain — instantly and directly to the user.

  • Real humans only – AI checks identity, motion, context and consistency.
  • Clear rules – each challenge has transparent criteria and reward logic.
  • Portable value – rewards can be saved, staked or spent inside the CHLG ecosystem.

The opportunity

Challenge culture already exists across TikTok, Instagram, sports and lifestyle. CHLG adds the missing reward layer and creates a new behavioral economy where real actions become an asset class.

What makes CHLG different?

CHLG is not another on-screen token – it is a real-world challenge economy where culture, AI and Web3 collide.

Real life first

CHLG pays for actions in the real world – not clicks, views or likes. Users earn by doing challenges they can feel: workouts, social dares, lifestyle missions and trend-driven tasks.

AI-verified proof-of-challenge

Every rewarded challenge passes through a multi-layer AI engine that checks face, motion, timing, camera behavior and metadata to confirm that a real human did the full challenge in one take.

Built on global trends

CHLG plugs directly into TikTok, Instagram and real-world trends. If it is already happening in culture, it can become a CHLG challenge – with rewards on top.

Brand-powered rewards

Brands and creators fund challenges by buying CHLG, turning marketing budgets into on-chain rewards for verified actions instead of untracked impressions.

Security & Fair Play

A challenge economy only works if users, brands and creators can trust the system.

Anti-cheat by design

Multi-layer AI makes it extremely hard to fake participation with deepfakes, old videos, bots or scripts. Suspicious submissions are rejected or routed to manual review.

Real users, real actions

Device- and behavior-level checks reduce farm-style activity and ensure that each reward is tied to a real person completing a real challenge.

Brand-safe environment

Sponsors know they are rewarding verified human actions instead of botted impressions, unlocking new types of performance-based campaigns.

On-chain transparency

Reward logic is enforced on-chain, and future audited smart contracts add an additional layer of trust for users, partners and investors.

Who is CHLG for?

CHLG is designed for the people who already live in challenge culture – we simply give them a way to earn from it.

Trend followers

People who love jumping on TikTok and Instagram trends can finally earn for doing the same challenges they already post for free.

Fitness & lifestyle doers

From daily pushups and cold showers to steps, runs and sports drills – CHLG turns discipline and healthy habits into rewards.

Creators & communities

Creators, teams and communities can launch their own challenge tracks, reward their followers with CHLG and plug into a shared global economy instead of building everything from scratch.

Brands & events

Brand marketers and event organizers can turn campaigns into measurable, verified actions – from product trials and attendance to user-generated content.

Creator Mode

Creators turn influence into real-world engagement.

Creator Mode allows influencers, athletes and lifestyle leaders to launch their own challenges and earn from real participation.

  • Publish custom challenges
  • Set rules, difficulty & reward tiers
  • Build streak-based communities
  • Earn a share of challenge engagement
  • Protected by CHLG AI anti-cheat engine

Tokenomics & Ecosystem

Fixed supply, user-first rewards and brand-powered demand, designed for long-term sustainable growth.

CHLG Token Utility

  • Reward currency for all AI‑verified challenges.
  • Streak and difficulty-based multipliers that scale earnings.
  • Creator Mode access — lock CHLG to run challenge funnels.
  • Brand challenges and sponsored missions funded by CHLG purchases.
  • Staking for higher-tier tasks, boosts and exclusive challenges.
  • AI verification credits — partners pay CHLG for face/motion/object checks.
  • Fee recycling: a % of fees is used for buyback or burn to support value.
  • Reputation & leveling — CHLG unlocks XP tiers and higher rewards.
  • Access to high-velocity challenges requiring minimum CHLG stake.
  • Ecosystem payments for challenge API, leaderboards and partner integrations.

Ecosystem Loop

  • Brands buy CHLG to fund challenge campaigns.
  • Users earn CHLG by completing real-world challenges.
  • Creators and power users stake or lock CHLG for higher tiers.
  • A share of platform fees is burned or recycled to support long-term value.
